<plot>The story of a neglectful father, and his estranged son set at the end of World War II. It is 1945 Germany. A Nazi soldier returns home to his childhood farm with the intent of convincing his father to retreat with him to Berlin. His father refuses. Old feelings rise to the surface, and suspicions grow until the son discovers that his father has been harboring a family of Jews. With the Russians en route they both must decide how far they are willing to go for their cause. Will their long buried love for each other emerge, or in their bitterness will they cling to their ideals?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?190920</url></doc>
